      • Serialized Fields

        • avgRating
          double avgRating
          The average customer rating given to this Movie.
        • cast
          String[] cast
          The casts of this Movie. The number of casts can be varied.
        • director
          String director
          The director of this Movie.
        • filename
          String filename
          The file path to this Movie's database.
        • isDeleted
          int isDeleted
          The index of the delete status of this Movie (0: not deleted, 1: deleted).
        • movieId
          int movieId
          The assigned id for this Movie. This is obtained from this Movie's index in the movie database.
        • movieRating
          int movieRating
          The index of the movie rating of this Movie (0: G, 1: PG, 2: M, 3: R16, 4: TBC).
        • movieType
          int movieType
          The index of the movie type of this Movie (0: 3D, 1: Blockbuster).
        • numReviews
          int numReviews
          The number of customer reviews for this Movie.
        • sales
          Double sales
          The total amount of movie spent on movie tickets for This Movie.
        • showStatus
          int showStatus
        • synopsis
          String synopsis
          The Synopsis of this Movie.
        • title
          String title
          The title of this Movie.
